org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.vector.keyseries

Interface VectorKeySeriesSerialized

  • All Superinterfaces:
    VectorKeySeries
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VectorKeySeriesBytesSerialized, VectorKeySeriesLongSerialized, VectorKeySeriesMultiSerialized, VectorKeySeriesSerializedImpl

    public interface VectorKeySeriesSerialized
extends VectorKeySeries
    An abstract adding serialization to key series. A key with no or some nulls has serialized bytes, offset, and length.
